Urban Cruiser 1.5 Xs MT – R267 800
Urban Cruiser 1.5 Xs AT – R289 000
Urban Cruiser 1.5 Xr MT – R294 500
Urban Cruiser 1.5 Xr AT – R315 700 All Urban Cruiser models are sold with a 3-services/45,000 km service plan. A 3-year/100,000 km warranty is also provided. Service intervals are pegged at 12 months/15,000 km. Read: Brace for more petrol price hikes in South Africa: economists